subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Graeme McDowell made seven birdies in an eight-hole stretch and shot an eight-under-par 63 to take the lead after two rounds of the O.H.L. Classic in Playa del Carmen, Mexico.
snippet: Graeme McDowell made seven birdies in an eight-hole stretch and shot an eight-under-par 63 to take the lead after two rounds of the O.H.L. Classic in Playa del Carmen, Mexico.
